    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
