    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in flawless condition. This example features the F22C1 longitudinal inline-four engine, renowned for its 8,200 RPM redline and high-compression VTEC engagement. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise, close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis retains its original X-bone frame integrity, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension at all four corners for unparalleled kinematic precision. Zero modifications, all matching VIN tags on body panels, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key, investment-quality roadster for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
