    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and garage-kept since day one. The exterior boasts a flawless deep-gloss finish with no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, reflecting its sheltered life. Inside, the premium leather interior remains in pristine condition, with every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, functioning perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history from authorized dealerships and a whisper-quiet engine that performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a top-tier example of this model, complete with all original keys, manuals, and documented maintenance logs. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, and the tires have significant tread remaining. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade vehicle.",
